{"tid":2357737,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高層大換血 胞妹金與正獲重用","createTime":"2021-01-07T15:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T15:47:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0aea51458467b3706f18474db2424517c49f46","tid":2357737,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210107/CWOWAWGUK5DQZDYRONGGGCACS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210107%2FCWOWAWGUK5DQZDYRONGGGCACS4%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z9KNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=23542084\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210107%2FCWOWAWGUK5DQZDYRONGGGCACS4%2F&h=54e61c87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210107/CWOWAWGUK5DQZDYRONGGGCACS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n高層大換血 胞妹金與正獲重用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/turRd1h26q0j2NeoLQ4MbYon3iI=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VWYUG4AKL5BX5I3FFZRXAVDM7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FturRd1h26q0j2NeoLQ4MbYon3iI%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVWYUG4AKL5BX5I3FFZRXAVDM7A.jpg&h=7c42ace0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大會現場座無虛設，沒有人戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n北韓勞動黨第八次全國代表大會高官雲集，外界發現與上屆2016年相比，39名高官中多達29人是新面孔；專家預料今屆大會將公佈更多高層人事調動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五年首次黨大會 稱經濟失策陷危機  金正恩憂失勢 認衰箍民心<br />\n<br />\n有份上台的領導層與四年前一樣是39人，但換血率高近75%，新亮相官員大多是金正恩認為過去五年工作成績優異、值得提拔的幹部，包括其胞妹、勞動黨第一副部長金與正，以及組織指導部第一副部長趙勇元。<br />\n<br />\n未被撤換的，包括北韓名義上的國家元首、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，無份上台的與會黨代表人選亦有明顯變化，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n軍代表大減 草根黨員倍增<br />\n<br />\n金正恩上台後，大肆革除其父、已故領袖金正日的多年親信，削弱原本權重的人民軍權力，並提拔他自己較年輕的親信，但有分析指，經濟官員和草根黨員的與會機會增加，反映他想將今屆大會塑造成振興北韓經濟的起點，以及傾聽普羅大眾之聲的機會。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/韓聯社"}]}